    {
      "type": "callout",
      "variant": "info",
      "title": "Events are the source of truth",
      "text": "The events JSONL format is versioned by the AgentEvent contract in types.ts. moat.json is fully re-derivable from events by running moatlog distill — events are the source of truth."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": ".moatlogignore"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": ".moatlogignore uses .gitignore syntax. Files matching patterns are excluded at the hook layer (never written to JSONL) and at the distill layer. moatlog init writes .moatlogignore automatically."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Default patterns (from DEFAULT_MOATLOGIGNORE_PATTERNS in packages/core/src/moatlogignore.ts, plus .moatlog/ added by init):"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "text",
      "code": ".env*\n*.pem\n*.key\nid_rsa*\n*credentials*\n.npmrc\n.moatlog/"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Verifying hooks are active"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "content": [
