    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Advanced users can edit the hook scripts in .cursor/hooks/ or .claude/hooks/ directly. moatlog init --force will overwrite customizations to those scaffolded files. If you need custom logic, keep it in a separate script and call it from the moatlog hook script."
